Nature Ecology and Evolution bụ akwụkwọ sayensị a na-enyocha kwa ọnwa n'ịntanetị nke Otu na-ebipụta ihe gbasara Nature bipụtara na-ekpuchi akụkụ niile nke nyocha gbasara gburugburu ebe obibi na evolushọn
Onye isi nchịkọta akụkọ mbụ na nke ugbu a bụ Patrick Goymer.
Dị ka Journal Citation Reports si kwuo, Nature Ecology na Evolution nwere mmetụta mmetụta nke afọ 2020 nke 15.46.
